lenders.occupational_info: For me, teaching has been about helping students see the possibilities life has for them and helping them with the skills they need to achieve their goals.  The goals of KIVA resonate with me in the same way.

lenders.name: Bernard
lenders.loan_because: I believe in the notion of being a citizen of the world; there are no borders.  I believe that everyone deserves a chance.  Because I live in a country that offers a lot, I want to give hope and help others who are less fortunate.  I like knowing that I am helping others get closer to living their dreams.

lenders.name: Janine
lenders.loan_because: I want to help and I believe in the power of people taking responsibility.
lenders.occupational_info: I help companies explain their products to their customers.
